    <description>Called as a subflow for handling all create, update, and delete actions for the Project Member object, running in System Context Without Sharing mode.  Input variables:  inputNotes, inputProjectId, inputProjectMemberId, inputRole, inputSelectedAction, inputSendEmail, and inputUserId.

To create PM, provide inputSelectedAction, inputProjectId, inputNotes, inputRole, inputSendEmail, and inputUserId.

To edit PM, provide inputSelectedAction, inputProjectId, inputProjectMemberId, inputNotes, and inputRole.

To delete PM, provide inputSelectedAction, inputProjectId, and inputProjectMemberId.

To delete all PMs for a project, provide inputSelectedAction and inputProjectId.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>fProjectMemberName</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(ISBLANK({!getUser.FirstName}), {!getUser.LastName}, {!getUser.FirstName} &amp; &quot; &quot; &amp; {!getUser.LastName})</expression>
    </formulas>
